{"pageProps":{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji50","name":"毛泽东全集第50卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji50.pdf"],"article":{"title":"关于武斗的指示","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于武斗的指示"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1967年8月）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对武斗不要看得太紧张，对形势不能看得太严重，不要急。那里有武斗，必然有后台，让他多表演一下，越表演越孤立，使群众看得更清楚，群众孤立他，就好办了。乱是暂时的，可以转化为好的。打架是支流，是暂时的支流。决不能转移斗争的大方向。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":8}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":65,"page_end":65},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"指示"}]}]},"__N_SSG":true}